commit.message:
Removed JSONForMirc

Updating ReadMe to show how to install it for those who still want to

Updated commands, bot should work now

Updated commands.

Integrated Michaella's commands into mine so now we can start and stop
contests at any time. Time has also been updated to reflect minutes and
seconds and you can now input links during the contest period.

Implemented Helper commands

hi - introductory message
!src - links user to imgur
!help - links to full command list
autoban functions

Added necessary files for project

Added dependency files, command for timer, and test command for loading
in art choices.
